表格派工单管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('DispatchOrder')
and type = 'U')
drop table DispatchOrder
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: DispatchOrder */
/*==============================================================*/
create table DispatchOrder (
ID int identity(1,1),
DO_No varchar(50) not null,
ProductNo varchar(12) not null,
ProductDesc varchar(400) null,
WorkOrderNo varchar(20) null,
MachineNo varchar(12) not null,
MouldNo varchar(12) not null,
StartDate datetime not null,
StopDate datetime not null,
ActualStartDate datetime null,
ActualStopDate datetime null,
BadQty int null constraint DF_DispatchOrder_BadQty default (0),
StandCycle int null,
MaxInjectionCycle int null,
MinInjectionCycle int null,
DispatchDate datetime null,
DispatchNum int null constraint DF_DispatchOrder_DispatchNum default (0),
Do_Num AS (DispatchNum),
CheckStatus int null,
DispatchStatus varchar(10) null constraint DF_DispatchOrder_DispatchState default (2),
Remark varchar(200) null,
UpdataCycleStatus int null,
GroupNum decimal null,
Creater varchar(50) null,
constraint PK_DISPATCHORDER primary key nonclustered ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'0:未审核
1:已审核
2:已完成生产或在生产',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'DispatchOrder', 'column', 'DispatchStatus'
go
